{"data": [{"id": "4747503", "title": "Major Signals Point To Market Top: Investment Risk Mitigation Is Prudent Now", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Price crash and bear market\" data-id=\"1079127056\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5354px\" height=\"3569px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">24K-Production</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Several valuation and behavioral indicators are signaling that a generational stock market top is forming. While periods of overvaluation can persist, we advise reducing equity exposure in the <a href=\"https://www.barrons.com/livecoverage/stock-market-today-122724/card/the-magnificent-seven-stocks-are-selling-off-qlZz7WDyJL9MCBZskXUs\" rel=\"nofollow\">Magnificent Seven</a>, capitalization weighted indices like the S&amp;P 500 (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747503-major-signals-point-to-market-top-investment-risk-mitigation-is-prudent-now", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 20:25:12", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747502", "title": "Silence Therapeutics: Simply No Match For Its Orally Dosed Rival (Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475830028/image_1475830028.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A single professional athlete covers her face in disappointment while sitting on the bench.\" data-id=\"1475830028\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475830028/image_1475830028.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475830028/image_1475830028.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475830028/image_1475830028.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475830028/image_1475830028.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475830028/image_1475830028.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475830028/image_1475830028.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475830028/image_1475830028.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475830028/image_1475830028.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Lighthouse Films/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Silence Therapeutics plc</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SLN\" title=\"Silence Therapeutics plc\">SLN</a></span>) dropped nearly 75% overnight on November 18 after presenting data from lead candidate Zerlasiran, a small-interfering RNA targeting Lipoprotein(a) reduction in patients. Looking through the data, I couldn\u2019t find the problem right away. Here</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475830028/image_1475830028.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747502-silence-therapeutics-simply-no-match-for-its-orally-dosed-rival-downgrade", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 20:18:36", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747501", "title": "Verastem: Planning The PDUFA Run-Up", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/543195141/image_543195141.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Caucasian woman running up staircase\" data-id=\"543195141\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/543195141/image_543195141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/543195141/image_543195141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/543195141/image_543195141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/543195141/image_543195141.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/543195141/image_543195141.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/