e Slump Was Justified", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2164284029/image_2164284029.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Luftaufnahme aus dem hohen Winkel des SoFi-Stadions bei Nacht\" data-id=\"2164284029\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"810px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2164284029/image_2164284029.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2164284029/image_2164284029.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2164284029/image_2164284029.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2164284029/image_2164284029.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2164284029/image_2164284029.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2164284029/image_2164284029.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2164284029/image_2164284029.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2164284029/image_2164284029.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">halbergman/iStock Unreleased via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Article Thesis</h2> <p>SoFi Technologies, Inc.'s (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SOFI\" title=\"SoFi Technologies, Inc.\">SOFI</a></span>) share price declined by almost 10% on Thursday, with shares now trading close to 20% below the recent high. On the other hand, SoFi Technologies has risen massively over the last year, rising</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2164284029/image_2164284029.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747499-sofi-price-slump-was-justified", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 19:32:49", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747497", "title": "2024 Performance Review & Lessons Learnt, +34% Annual Return, +40% CAGR In 5 Years", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1772169250/image_1772169250.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"New Year\" data-id=\"1772169250\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1049px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1772169250/image_1772169250.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1772169250/image_1772169250.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1772169250/image_1772169250.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1772169250/image_1772169250.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1772169250/image_1772169250.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1772169250/image_1772169250.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1772169250/image_1772169250.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1772169250/image_1772169250.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Thanakorn Piadaeng/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><span>Another year has come and gone, and another year of portfolio performance to reflect on.</span></p> <p><span>2024 was a great year for many US and Canadian indices, many returning double digit returns.</span></p> <ul> <li><span>Dow Jones (</span></li> </ul>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1772169250/image_1772169250.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747497-2024-performance-review-and-lessons-learnt-plus-34-percent-annual-return-plus-40-percent-cagr-in-5-years", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 19:21:58", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747496", "title": "Michelin: Aging Car Population Is A Plus To Add", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458639773/image_458639773.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Michelin Tire\" data-id=\"458639773\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4912px\" height=\"3264px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458639773/image_458639773.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458639773/image_458639773.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458639773/image_458639773.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458639773/image_458639773.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458639773/image_458639773.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458639773/image_458639773.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458639773/image_458639773.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458639773/image_458639773.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">kenneth-cheung</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Following a minus 8.14% since our <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4703690-michelin-stock-earnings-upside-impressive-capital-allocation-policies\">July 2024 update</a> (Fig 1), we see an opportunity to add to Compagnie G\u00e9n\u00e9rale des \u00c9tablissements Michelin (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MGDDF#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\">OTCPK:MGDDF</a>)(<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MGDDY#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\">OTCPK:MGDDY</a>), one of the world's largest tire producers. Considering the company's 2024</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458639773/image_458639773.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747496-michelin-aging-car-population-is-a-plus-to-add", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 19:14:36", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747477", "title": "2024 Macro Commentary: Next Economy Forces Reshaping Markets", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business finance and investment, Analyze economic growth charts for informed business finance decisions and financial decision-making. Stock Market report, Strategy, Data Collection, Forecasting\" data-id=\"2021524839\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"910px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seeking